data.description: ** Renovated & Move in Ready w/clear CO** Charmed with modern characters,  two properties on one parcel in Prime Location!! Featuring 4 bedrooms with 2.5 baths! Front property featuring a living and dining room.  New kitchen with ample cabinets, granite counters & classy tile backsplash. New half  bath for your convenience on the main level. The 2nd floor has 2 spacious bedrooms with a new bath. The attic has 1 brand new bedroom and an unfinished storage room. Modern painting throughout w/neutral colors, new carpeting, new floors! Brand new windows in most of the home, new electrical throughout . Rear property features 1 bedroom, living room , kitchen and full bath. Additional parking space located in the rear. Great location for easy commute and walking distance to public transportation, shopping, schools, highways. This is a turnkey ready home!!
